{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"launch","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"files"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ListRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib7ListRefV"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"context"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19AppLaunchContextRefV","text":"AppLaunchContextRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/AppLaunchContextRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To launch the application without arguments pass a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"files","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" list."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that even if the launch is successful the application launched"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can fail to start if it runs into problems during startup. There is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"no way to detect this.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some URIs can be changed when passed through a GFile (for instance"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"unsupported URIs with strange formats like mailto:), so if you have","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"a textual URI you want to pass in as argument, consider using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.AppInfo.launch_uris"},{"type":"text","text":"] instead."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The launched application inherits the environment of the launching","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"process, but it can be modified with [method"},{"code":"Gio.AppLaunchContext.setenv","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.AppLaunchContext.unsetenv"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On UNIX, this function sets the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GIO_LAUNCHED_DESKTOP_FILE"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"environment variable with the path of the launched desktop file and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GIO_LAUNCHED_DESKTOP_FILE_PID"},{"text":" to the process id of the launched","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"process. This can be used to ignore "},{"code":"GIO_LAUNCHED_DESKTOP_FILE","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"should it be inherited by further processes. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"DISPLAY","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"XDG_ACTIVATION_TOKEN"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"DESKTOP_STARTUP_ID","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" environment"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"variables are also set, based on information provided in "},{"code":"context","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Launches the application. Passes "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"files"},{"type":"text","text":" to the launched application"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as arguments, using the optional ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"context"},{"type":"text","text":" to get information"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"about the details of the launcher (like what screen it is on)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"On error, "},{"code":"error","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set accordingly."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/osxappinfo\/launch(files:context:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfo","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfo\/AppInfoProtocol-Implementations"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfo\/launch(files:context:)"},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:3GIO15AppInfoProtocolPAAE6launch5files7contextSb4GLib7ListRefVSg_AA0b13LaunchContextJ0VSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO10OsxAppInfoC","title":"launch(files:context:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"launch"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"files"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib7ListRefV","text":"ListRef"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"context","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19AppLaunchContextRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AppLaunchContextRef"},{"text":"?) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OsxAppInfo":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OsxAppInfo","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OsxAppInfo","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OsxAppInfo","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/do